    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Ice Bombs are palm-sized, spherical, and extremely deadly explosive Cold based weapons.</p><p> In addition to being surprisingly powerful for their size, they can only be turned off by whoever turned them on.</p><p> Ice Bombs have a range equal to 30 feet + your Strength modifier x 5.</p><p> As an action, you can throw an Ice Bomb at a point you can see within range.</p><p> Each creature within 10 feet must make a Constitution saving throw.</p><p> A creature takes Cold damage and gains one rank of the chilled condition until the end of their next turn on a failed save, or half as much damage and no additional effects as on a successful one.</p>",
